## 🔹 CALCULATIONS TO MAKE

**Booking Conversion Rate**
= (Successful bookings / Booking-intent calls) × 100

**Lost Revenue Estimate**
= Lost bookings × Average party size × Average cover value
(Use £45/cover for fine dining, £25/cover for casual if not specified)

**Transfer Rate**
= (Calls transferred to human / Total calls) × 100

**Peak Demand Index**
= Calls in busiest hour / Average hourly calls

**Advance Booking Window**
= Average days between call date and requested booking date

